							<h2>Facebook App Development</h2>
							<p>With over one billion users worldwide, Facebook is the world's largest social networking site. Businesses have started using Facebook as a highly effective advertising and marketing tool. In 2007, Facebook joined the mobile web and 6 years later over 100 million people access Facebook on their mobile devices and Smartphones. With such a wide database of customers at their fingertips, businesses are doing their best and setting up cutting edge strategies to leverage the power of Facebook.</p>
							<p>What makes your business' Facebook profile more visible are interesting, engaging, and interactive apps.  Find out how your business can benefit from successful Facebook app development.</p>
							<p><strong>What is Facebook App Development</strong></p>
							<p>Facebook app development is the creation of application software that can run on various mobile operating systems.</p>
							<p><strong>Benefits of Facebook App Development:</strong></p>
							<p>With the number of Facebook users growing daily, there are number of benefits of Facebook app development and some of them are:</p>
							<p><strong>Brand Awareness and Brand Reputation </strong></p>
							<p>Designing customizable Facebook apps help increase your brand awareness. You can take your business to people from all demographics and age groups.  Facebook takes you right to your customers and brings your customers right to you. You have instant access to what people are saying about your products and service and respond accordingly.</p>
							<p><strong>Boosts Traffic to Your Site </strong></p>
							<p>Using different Facebook apps can help direct more traffic to your company website. Customers that click on your page banners, links, and images can learn more about your service offerings.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6 mobile-content">
							<p><strong>An Effective Tool to Study Customer Behavior</strong></p>
